=== For Loop Test ===
for loop: i = 0, loopVar = 0, outerVar = 100
for loop: i = 1, loopVar = 10, outerVar = 100
for loop: i = 2, loopVar = 20, outerVar = 100
after for loop: outerVar = 100
=== While Loop Test ===
while loop: counter = 0, loopVar = 0, outerVar = 200
while loop: counter = 1, loopVar = 20, outerVar = 200
while loop: counter = 2, loopVar = 40, outerVar = 200
after while loop: outerVar = 200, counter = 3
=== Do-While Loop Test ===
do-while loop: counter = 0, loopVar = 0, outerVar = 300
do-while loop: counter = 1, loopVar = 30, outerVar = 300
do-while loop: counter = 2, loopVar = 60, outerVar = 300
after do-while loop: outerVar = 300, counter = 3
=== Nested Loop Test ===
outer loop: i = 0, outerLoopVar = 0
  inner loop: j = 0, innerLoopVar = 0, outerLoopVar = 0
  inner loop: j = 1, innerLoopVar = 10, outerLoopVar = 0
outer loop: i = 1, outerLoopVar = 100
  inner loop: j = 0, innerLoopVar = 0, outerLoopVar = 100
  inner loop: j = 1, innerLoopVar = 10, outerLoopVar = 100